{"tid":1642622,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"小心．講錢傷感情","createTime":"2019-10-09T19:46:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T19:53:41.000Z","uid":292155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4264c9a9daaadfad367271b392dc6f1c6ec2d3ec","tid":1642622,"uid":292155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T19:46:14.000Z","msg":"我喺WeChat 朋友圈，見到<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">李力持導演</span></strong> post 咗呢封<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">勒索信</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RZfpY0P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRZfpY0P.jpg&h=a755ef32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一直冇大台，何來有個<strong>［勇武䕶港聯盟］</strong>代表勇武手足呢？<br />\n<br />\n大家小心，<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍色陣營</span>已派一班人假裝一眾和勇手足，發電郵四圍勒索商戶、甚至逐家逐戶拍門收取保護費。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">共產黨</span>，依家大玩<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">「講錢傷感情」</span></strong>呢個人性弱點。<br />\n<br />\n目的係，加劇香港市民對和勇因財失義嘅擔憂，令民意逆轉。<br />\n<br />\n當然，我相信廣大香港市民，絕對唔會咁戇居中招...<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S. 封信，我懷疑係李力持親自編寫，因為封信嘅一字一句都～真係笑話～<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dbf0b8ee44a7bf16cf9ae52234ae681cf6f44af","tid":1642622,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T19:53:41.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係星火同612<br />\n唔好上當呀各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}